# ── Mock mode ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Set to "true" to run the frontend with mock data (no DB or API server needed).
# All 8 features are covered: schemas, tables, fields, wide tables, versions,
# analysis, naming dictionary, and rules.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and toggle as needed:
#   VITE_USE_MOCK=true   → mock data, works offline
#   VITE_USE_MOCK=false  → real API at http://localhost:3005
VITE_USE_MOCK=false
